00:04.571 --> 00:06.572
<i>Danny and Polly</i>
<i>found themselves in love</i>

00:06.573 --> 00:08.073
<i>and found out that most people</i>

00:08.074 --> 00:10.075
<i>found their relationship</i>
<i>unusual.</i>

00:10.076 --> 00:13.078
<i>Dutch found a note from Eunice,</i>
<i>saying she'd found another man,</i>

00:13.079 --> 00:14.079
<i>run off with him,</i>

00:14.080 --> 00:16.081
<i>and Dutch better not</i>
<i>try and find her.</i>

00:16.082 --> 00:17.583
<i>Jessica found a psychiatrist</i>

00:17.584 --> 00:20.586
<i>to help her over her depression</i>
<i>she found herself in</i>

00:20.587 --> 00:21.587
<i>after she threw Chester out</i>

00:21.588 --> 00:23.088
<i>when she found out</i>

00:23.089 --> 00:25.090
<i>he was in love</i>
<i>with the minister's daughter.</i>

00:25.091 --> 00:26.592
<i>Carol and her cowboy boyfriend</i>

00:26.593 --> 00:29.094
<i>found themselves in New York</i>
<i>for the rodeo,</i>

00:29.095 --> 00:31.096
<i>and Jodie found himself</i>

00:31.097 --> 00:32.598
<i>agreeing to let her</i>
<i>see the baby.</i>

00:32.598 --> 00:34.099
<i>And Burt found out</i>

00:34.100 --> 00:35.601
<i>he's not going to die after all.</i>

00:35.602 --> 00:37.102
<i>Find it confusing?</i>

00:37.103 --> 00:40.106
<i>You won't</i>
<i>after this episode of...</i> Soap.

