<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:47.614 --> 00:49.615
<i>Jessica Tate...</i>

00:49.616 --> 00:52.117
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:52.118 --> 00:55.621
<i>These are the Tates...</i>

00:55.622 --> 00:59.124
<i>and these are the Campbells...</i>

